你現在需求一樣是：

HRS_CIP_TemplateMappings 裡，只要資料存在於 VERIFY..HRS_CIP_TemplateMappings，就刪掉。

先跑確認筆數版本：

SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM HRS_CIP_TemplateMappings A
INNER JOIN VERIFY..HRS_CIP_TemplateMappings B
    ON ISNULL(A.HRSQueryId,0) = ISNULL(B.HRSQueryId,0)
    AND ISNULL(A.CIPQueryId,0) = ISNULL(B.CIPQueryId,0)
    AND ISNULL(A.CIP_CustomerType,'') = ISNULL(B.CIP_CustomerType,'')
    AND ISNULL(A.HRSTemplateId,0) = ISNULL(B.HRSTemplateId,0)
    AND ISNULL(A.TemplateAnswerType,'') = ISNULL(B.TemplateAnswerType,'')
    AND ISNULL(A.OptionList,'') = ISNULL(B.OptionList,'')
    AND ISNULL(A.OptionCode,'') = ISNULL(B.OptionCode,'');

確認數量正確後，再執行刪除：

BEGIN TRAN;
DELETE A
FROM HRS_CIP_TemplateMappings A
INNER JOIN VERIFY..HRS_CIP_TemplateMappings B
    ON ISNULL(A.HRSQueryId,0) = ISNULL(B.HRSQueryId,0)
    AND ISNULL(A.CIPQueryId,0) = ISNULL(B.CIPQueryId,0)
    AND ISNULL(A.CIP_CustomerType,'') = ISNULL(B.CIP_CustomerType,'')
    AND ISNULL(A.HRSTemplateId,0) = ISNULL(B.HRSTemplateId,0)
    AND ISNULL(A.TemplateAnswerType,'') = ISNULL(B.TemplateAnswerType,'')
    AND ISNULL(A.OptionList,'') = ISNULL(B.OptionList,'')
    AND ISNULL(A.OptionCode,'') = ISNULL(B.OptionCode,'');
-- 先確認刪除筆數
SELECT @@ROWCOUNT AS DeletedRows;
ROLLBACK;

如果 DeletedRows 正確：

把最後：

